  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Arrange the toasted bread on a baking sheet.",
    "Drizzle olive oil over the bread and sprinkle with gochugaru and crushed red pepper.",
    "Bake for 5 minutes, or until the bread is crispy and slightly puffed.",
    "Meanwhile, mix together minced garlic and lemon juice in a small bowl.",
    "Remove the bread from the oven and brush the garlic-lemon mixture over each slice.",
    "Top each slice with a sprinkle of chopped cilantro and a crumble of feta cheese.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
